A chieftain of the ruling All Progressives Congress, APC, and the Chief Whip of the Senate, Orji Uzor Kalu, says the Labour Party presidential candidate has uncommon wisdom. The former Governor of Abia State stated this in a post on his official social media handles while congratulating Obi on his 61st birthday. Obi who was born on July 19, 1961, will clock 61 years on Tuesday (today). Senator Kalu, in the felicitation post, wished Obi good health and peace of mind. The post reads, “I wish my dear brother and Presidential Candidate of Labour Party, Mr Peter Obi a very happy birthday. “You have exhibited uncommon wisdom, remarkable vision, and exemplary leadership. I wish you peace, good health, and happiness. Congratulations and happy birthday!”